\id 1JN - Uare
\h 1Ioane
\toc3 1Ioa
\toc2 1Ioane
\toc1 Ioaneꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\mt1 1Ioane
\mt2 Ioaneꞌa Mirihiroteꞌe Soꞌaḡa Ibiꞌa
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa
\ip Soꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Ioaneꞌa mirihiro. Aniꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga. Aniꞌe ibite Iesu hari manoḡa zuni mirihiro. Soꞌa ꞌahi zamaḡano Iesuꞌe agaḡa huga zu Badiꞌa Ubuga rae fureranadu aniꞌe ḡabofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae ihoziro. Emeꞌe Badiꞌa zu Iesu zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa zeḡe teite unihiꞌuma, ebu emeḡe nabudi zuni zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa zeḡe teite unihiꞌuma rae ḡoeriro. Ḡuriro ihore azaḡaniꞌa Iesuꞌe ahirio mene ariro, rehano vineo daꞌo ariro rae veꞌone ihoziroteꞌe moneo zeḡe ihoreꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureniro.
\c 1
\s1 Ḡabone Ziniꞌeteꞌe Ḡoeꞌa
\p 
\v 1 Emeꞌa ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa moneo zae mazao rae fureneꞌohe. Ḡoere aꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo onao izidi radiuꞌohe. Emeꞌa ḡoere eꞌe igiro, ebu emeḡe ubuma hina horoniro, zu ḡianiro, ebu emeḡe ꞌevore hina oboniro.
\v 2 Ḡabone eꞌeꞌa fureraro. Emeꞌe ani horoniro ebu ani moneo rae fureneꞌohe, ebu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu eꞌe moneo zae mazao harameꞌohe. Ḡabone tuḡutuḡu aꞌe Moga teite radiunu ebu emeḡe mazao fureraro.
\v 3 Zae zuni emeḡe teite unihifine, eme emeḡeꞌa nagini horoniroteꞌe zu igiroteꞌe zae mazao rae fureneꞌohe. Emeꞌa unihotiteꞌetaꞌaꞌe Moga zu Ubuga, Iesu Keriso teite unihotiteꞌohe.
\v 4 Emeḡe niduꞌa tiburu matuꞌe rudanoga veize emeꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌe Agaḡa
\p 
\v 5 Emeꞌa Iesuonoꞌo egadu zae mazao rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe. Badiꞌaꞌe agaḡa. Ani mazaoꞌe uzabo oꞌoꞌa hune.
\v 6 Emeꞌa, “Badiꞌa teite uniheꞌohe,” rae raenaꞌa, ꞌize uzabo zamaḡano radiune, eme ḡurireꞌohe zu ḡoere hugano mene radiuꞌohe.
\v 7 Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa agaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe teige, emeꞌa agaḡano radiune, emeꞌe unihotitiꞌuma zu ane Ubuga Iesu ruḡaniꞌa haḡaife sauꞌa niduꞌaonoꞌo emeḡe vuzuꞌe dehefiꞌuma.
\v 8 Emeꞌa haḡaife sauꞌa oꞌoꞌa rae reine, eme emeḡeꞌa bare soꞌofeꞌohe zu ḡoere hugano mene radiuꞌohe.
\v 9 Rehano emeꞌa haḡaife sauꞌa Badiꞌa mazao rae furenine, haḡaife sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma zu emeꞌa mene duduḡano haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡanonoꞌo vuzuꞌe dehefiꞌuma. Mazaḡa aniꞌe zama niduꞌa hina haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zu haḡai duduḡa daꞌo haḡaeꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.
\v 10 Badiꞌaꞌe, “Vaze niduꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌohe,” rae raꞌohe. Rehano emeꞌa, “Haḡai sauꞌa mene haḡairo,” rae reine, eme, “Badiꞌaꞌe ḡuriro Badiꞌaḡa,” rae raꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Ebu ani ḡoereꞌe emeḡe zamao mene radiuꞌohe.
\c 2
\s1 Kerisoꞌe Danafeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa
\p 
\v 1 Eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa, za haḡai sauꞌa mene haḡaifine eḡeꞌa zae veize ꞌahi miriheꞌohe. Rehano emeḡe boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌetene, emeḡe veize Moga mazao bire ḡoereꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe emeḡe teite radiuꞌohe. Aniꞌe vaze duduḡa, Iesu Keriso.
\v 2 Aniꞌe emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modifine ane bare dibuꞌiro. Mene emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa uꞌano daꞌo, rehano habaꞌahabaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌa haḡaize sauꞌa uꞌano ꞌougiro.
\p 
\v 3 Emeꞌa Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa egohaune, emeꞌa ani edereꞌetaꞌaꞌe edere huniꞌuma.
\v 4 Iniuꞌa, “E Badiꞌa edeḡa,” rae raenaꞌa, ane goro ḡoeꞌa mene egohaune, aniꞌe ḡuriro vazeḡa zu ḡoere hugano mene radiuꞌohe.
\v 5 Rehano iniuꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere egohaune, ani zamaḡa niduꞌa hina hube hune Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe ihozeꞌohe. ꞌOugadu emeꞌe Badiꞌa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe edereꞌohe.
\v 6 Iniu Badiꞌa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa haḡairoteꞌe teige haḡaeꞌenaꞌa radiꞌuma.
\s1 Goro Ḡoeꞌa Iziga
\p 
\v 7 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, eḡeꞌa zae veize miriheꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene goro ḡoeꞌa iziga, rehano aꞌe zaeꞌa ibite Iesu mazao fie ḡadaheniroteꞌe madaḡano meiroteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌa amahiḡa. Goro ḡoeꞌa amahiḡaꞌe zaeꞌa igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.
\v 8 Rehano e zae veize goro ḡoeꞌa iziga ꞌahoga miriheꞌohe. Goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌahiꞌe Kerisoꞌa hugano hegote radiro, zu zae zuni hugano hegote radiuꞌohe. Mazaḡa uzaboꞌe dauḡeꞌohe ebu agaḡa hugaꞌe amahi aradu agaru radiuꞌohe.
\v 9 Iniuꞌa, “E agaḡano radiuꞌohe,” rae raenaꞌa, ane negoḡa nabuga heꞌeheꞌezeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌize uzaboḡano radiuꞌohe.
\v 10 Iniu ane negoḡa nabuga zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe agaḡano radiuꞌohe, ebu ani mae buneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡani ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\v 11 Rehano iniu ane negoḡa nabuga heꞌeheꞌezeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe uzaboḡano radiuꞌohe ebu uzaboḡano ragaveꞌohe. Ani aneꞌa noꞌe onameꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa, mazaḡa uzaboꞌa ubumaḡa kuruniro.
\p 
\v 12 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa Keriso niḡano zae haḡai sauꞌa rae modiro.
\p 
\v 13 Mama niduꞌa, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso edeḡa.
\p Tahiꞌa iziga, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌa sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Satani raharahaniro.
\p 
\v 14 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe emeḡe Mama edeḡa.
\p Mama niduꞌa, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso edeḡa.
\p Tahiꞌa iziga, e zae veize miriheꞌohe, mazaḡa zaꞌe inaraḡa, zu Badiꞌa ḡoereꞌe zae zamao radiuꞌohe, zu zaꞌa sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Satani raharahaniro.
\p 
\v 15 Raha ꞌahi ga raha ḡauḡa ago zamare borofoꞌi. Iniu raha ꞌahi zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Mama mene zamare borofeꞌohe.
\v 16 Mazaḡa raha ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe Mama mazaonoꞌo mene areꞌohe, rehano raha ꞌahaonoꞌo areꞌohe. Raha ḡauḡaꞌe ahiri ura haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa, zu ubuma hina horonadu haḡai sauꞌa haḡaihi rae raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡa, zu ze zeḡeꞌa bare maꞌora azaḡa rae niguzeꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 17 Raha ꞌahi zu raha azaḡaniꞌa urateꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe dauḡeꞌohe, rehano iniu Badiꞌa ura haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu.
\s1 Keriso Agire Azaḡa
\p 
\v 18 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, izidiꞌe mada ḡonaga. Za Keriso agire azaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma rae igiroteꞌe teige, ane agire azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa aradu izidi radiuꞌohe. Eꞌe uꞌano, eme izidiꞌe mada ḡonaga rae edereꞌohe.
\v 19 Zeꞌa emeḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡiniro, mazaḡa ze mene hube hune emeḡe none azaḡa reiro. Zeꞌe emeḡe none azaḡa reifone, emeḡe teite radifo. Ze emeḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡiniroteꞌeꞌa zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe mene emeḡe none azaḡa rae deheru ihofiro.
\p 
\v 20 Rehano zaeꞌa Zaḡoḡa Vazeḡaonoꞌo Vine Zaḡoḡa meiro,\f + \fr 2:20 \fqa Zaḡoḡa Vazeḡaniꞌa zae vadinize rana dehoro beꞌuniro\f* ebu zae niduꞌaꞌe ḡoere huga edereꞌohe.
\v 21 E zae veize miriheꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene mazaḡa zaꞌe ḡoere huga aḡuꞌa. Zaꞌe ḡoere huga edeḡa zu ḡoere huganonoꞌo ḡuriroꞌa mene fureruꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Eꞌe uꞌano, e ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.
\v 22 Ḡuriro vazeḡaꞌe iniu? Aꞌe, “Iesuꞌe Keriso,” rae raꞌeteꞌe oꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa! ꞌUguḡa vazeḡaꞌe Keriso agire vazeḡa, ebu Moga zu Ubuga oꞌozeꞌohe.
\v 23 Ubuga oꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao Mogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa. Ubuga mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao Moga zuni eꞌe.
\p 
\v 24 Zaeꞌa ḡadaheḡano igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zamazeo obone giganoꞌi. Ḡadaheḡano igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe zamazeo radiune, zae zuni Ubuga ebu Moga teite tiburanadu radiꞌuma.
\v 25 Aꞌe aniꞌa emeḡe teite ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ebu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu.
\p 
\v 26 E iniu za soꞌozadu tutuze veꞌozihi rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa moneo zae veize ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.
\v 27 Zaꞌe Kerisoꞌa ziniroteꞌe Vineḡa Zaḡoḡa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo za vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa za ihozoga veize mene umideꞌohe. Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡau niduꞌa moneo za ihozeꞌohe. Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa nagini ihozeꞌetaꞌaꞌe huga zu mene ḡuriro. Ane ihore idunaḡano Keriso teite tiburanadu radoꞌi.
\p 
\v 28 Eꞌanoꞌo, tahiꞌatahiꞌa, Keriso teite tiburanadu radoꞌi. ꞌOugine, aniꞌa bare arine, ani ubumao mene rihaꞌuma, ebu aniꞌa ariteꞌe madaḡano ani ubumao mene mazagaroziꞌuma.
\v 29 Za aniꞌe duduḡa rae ederine, haḡai duduḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga rae reirotaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma.
\c 3
\s1 Badiꞌa Ubugaubuga
\p 
\v 1 Emeḡe Mamaꞌa eme zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe moneo zamaroꞌi. Aniꞌa emeḡe ufeta zamareꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, emeꞌe ane ubugaubuga rae hufadu emeꞌe ane ubugaubuga rae raꞌohe. Raha azaḡaniꞌa Badiꞌa mene ederiroteꞌe uꞌano eme mene edeḡa.
\v 2 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, izidi emeꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga. Zama moneo emeꞌe nouge reiteꞌe ꞌize mene deheru edereꞌohe. Rehano eme edeḡa, Kerisoꞌa raha ꞌadao arine emeꞌe ani teigiꞌuma, mazaḡa eme aniꞌe iniu rae huga horoniꞌuma.
\v 3 Iesuꞌa ariteꞌe horonoga guhineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Kerisoꞌe deheḡa hune teige, ze zeḡeꞌa bare dehezeꞌohe.
\p 
\v 4 Iniu haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌohe. Haḡai sauꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa varadeꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe.
\v 5 Za Iesuꞌa haḡai sauꞌa mae vaḡinifine raha ꞌadao furerarotaꞌaꞌe edeḡa. Ani mazao haḡai sauꞌaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\v 6 Iniu ani teite tiburanadu radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa mene ꞌaune haḡaeꞌohe. Iniu haḡai sauꞌa ꞌaune haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iesu mene horoniro zu mene ederiro.
\p 
\v 7 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, iniuꞌa za soꞌozoga gararoꞌi. Kerisoꞌe duduḡa teige, iniu haḡai duduḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zuni Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa.
\v 8 Haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Diabolo mone vazeḡa, mazaḡa Diaboloꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo haḡai sauꞌa haḡae areꞌohe. Diabolo gauḡa ruinoga veize Badiꞌa Ubuganiꞌa ariro.
\v 9 Badiꞌa ubugaubugaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa mene ꞌaune haḡaeꞌohe, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa ḡabone iziga ezoneḡa zenadu ezone eꞌeꞌa zamazeo radiuꞌohe. Ze haḡai sauꞌa ꞌaune haḡaogaꞌe mene idaḡa, mazaḡa zeꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubugano reiro.
\v 10 Eꞌe uꞌano, eme iniuꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga, ebu iniuꞌe Diabolo ubugaubuga rae deheru edereꞌohe. Iniu haḡai duduḡa mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe zu negoḡa nabuga mene zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene Badiꞌa ubuga.
\s1 Zamarotitoꞌi
\p 
\v 11 Eme zamarotitiꞌuma. Aꞌe zaeꞌa ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo igiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.
\v 12 Eme Kaino mene teigiꞌuma. Aniꞌe sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Satani mone vazeḡa radu ane negoḡa maro. Nougadu aniꞌa negoḡa maro? Mazaḡa ane haḡaiꞌe sauꞌa, u negoḡa haḡaiꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa.
\v 13 Nego nabudi, raha azaḡaniꞌa za heꞌeheꞌezoꞌidene, ago zaguzaganoꞌi.
\v 14 Emeꞌa runeonoꞌo vaḡinadu ḡabone meirotaꞌaꞌe eme edeḡa, mazaḡa emeḡe nego nabudi zamare borofeꞌohe. Iniu negoḡa nabuga mene zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ruga.
\v 15 Iniu ane negoḡa nabuga heꞌeheꞌezeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe vaze mauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Zaꞌe edeḡa, vaze mauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao ḡabone tuḡutuḡuꞌe oꞌoꞌa.
\p 
\v 16 Kerisoꞌa emeḡe veize ḡaboneḡa ahetiro. ꞌOugadu emeꞌa nougenouge vaze zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiro. Eꞌanoꞌo eme zuni nego nabudi veize ḡabonefe ahetiꞌuma.
\v 17 Raha toheḡa ḡehaḡa meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa negoḡa nabuga mazao ḡau ꞌahoga ferezeꞌeteꞌe horoneꞌe rehano, mene vetuḡazeadu mene danazine, aniꞌe Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌohe rae reꞌumahe?
\v 18 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, eme hebe ga ḡoere hina daꞌo mene zamarotitiꞌuma, rehano haḡaife hina zu hugano zamarotitiꞌuma.
\v 19 ꞌOugine, eme emeḡeꞌa ḡoere huga hegoteꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederiꞌuma, ebu Badiꞌa ubumao mene rihauꞌenaꞌa, zama roḡeḡano edaꞌuma.
\v 20 Emeḡe zamaꞌa emeꞌe veꞌoḡa rae reine zuni, eme mene rihaꞌuma, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌe ḡihiꞌaḡa zu zamafe ufeta vitinoga. Aniꞌe ḡau niduꞌa edereꞌohe.
\p 
\v 21 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, emeḡe zamaꞌa emeꞌe veꞌoḡa rae mene reine, emeꞌe mene rihauꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa ubumao edaꞌuma.
\v 22 Ebu emeꞌa nagini umideꞌeteꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo hidiꞌuma, mazaḡa ane goro ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌohe zu ani matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa haḡaeꞌohe.
\v 23 Ani goro ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Ane Ubuga Iesu Keriso mazao fiꞌuma ebu aniꞌa ḡoere riḡa ifiroteꞌe teige, nego nabudi zamarotitiꞌuma.
\v 24 Iniu Keriso goro ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ani teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe zu aniꞌe zeḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe. Kerisoꞌa emeḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe aniꞌa rifiroteꞌe Vineḡa Zaḡoḡa uꞌano edereꞌohe.
\c 4
\s1 Vine Zaḡoḡa zu Ḡuriro Viga
\p 
\v 1 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, “Badiꞌa Vineꞌe eḡe mazao,” rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ago mae ḡihizoꞌi. Zeḡe ḡoereꞌe Badiꞌa Vineonoꞌo ga meneꞌe ederifine tuhuzoꞌi. Mazaḡa ḡuriro peroveta azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa raha ꞌadao fureraro.
\v 2 Badiꞌa Vineꞌe iniu mazao radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ꞌahige ederiꞌuma: Iniu Iesu Kerisoꞌa ahirio ariroteꞌe mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa Vineꞌe zeḡe mazao radiuꞌohe.
\v 3 Rehano Iesu mene mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazao Badiꞌa Vineꞌe oꞌoꞌa. ꞌUguḡa vazeḡa vineꞌe Keriso agirohauꞌohe. Zaꞌe Keriso agirohauꞌeteꞌe viganiꞌa ariteꞌe igiro. Aꞌe amahi aradu izidi raha ꞌadao radiuꞌohe.
\p 
\v 4 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, zaꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa, ebu ḡuriro peroveta azaḡa raharahaziro. Mazaḡa zae teite tiburanadu ḡabode radiuꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa Vigaꞌe raha ꞌadi viga ufeta vitine ḡihiꞌaḡa.
\v 5 Ḡuriro peroveta azaḡaꞌe raha mone azaḡa, eꞌanoꞌo raha ḡauḡa moneo ḡoereꞌohe zu raha azaḡaniꞌa zeḡe ḡoere igiꞌohe.
\v 6 Rehano emeꞌe Badiꞌa mone azaḡa. Iniu Badiꞌa edereꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe emeḡe ḡoere igiꞌohe. Rehano Badiꞌa mene mone vazeḡaꞌe emeḡe ḡoere mene igiꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo eme edeḡa, naginiꞌe ḡoere huga ihofeꞌeteꞌe Viga zu naginiꞌe ḡuriro viga.
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Eme Zamare Borofeꞌeteꞌe teige Zamarotitoꞌi
\p 
\v 7 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, eme zamarotitihi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa danafadu eme zamarotitogaꞌe idaḡa. Vaze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga, ebu Badiꞌa edeḡa.
\v 8 Vaze mene zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌe vaze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa.
\v 9 Badiꞌaꞌa eme zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe emeḡe mazao ꞌahige fureniro: Aniꞌa ane Ubuga tibuhuga raha ꞌadao tuḡuniro. Ubuga uꞌano, emeꞌe ḡabode radiuꞌohe.
\v 10 Zamarone hugaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Emeꞌe Badiꞌa mene zamare borofiro, rehano Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe zamare borofiro, ebu emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modadu ḡabofoga veize ane Ubuga tuḡunadu dibuꞌiro.
\v 11 Eḡe zamarone azaḡa, Badiꞌaꞌa eme ꞌouge ufeta zamare borofiro ꞌahine, eme zuni zamarotitiꞌuma.
\v 12 Vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa Badiꞌa mene horoniro. Rehano emeꞌa zamarotiteꞌeteꞌea Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe. Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, emeꞌa zamafe niduꞌa hina hube hune vaze zamare borofogaꞌe idaḡa.
\p 
\v 13 Eme edeḡa, Badiꞌaꞌa ane Vine rifiroteꞌe uꞌano, emeꞌe Badiꞌa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe zu aniꞌe emeḡe teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe.
\v 14 Moganiꞌa ane Ubugaꞌe raha azaḡa ḡaboziteꞌe vazeḡano reifine tuḡuniro. Eme eꞌe horoniro zu rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 15 Iniuꞌa Iesuꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa teite Badiꞌaꞌa tiburanadu radiuꞌohe, zu aniꞌe Badiꞌa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe.
\v 16 Emeꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edereꞌohe zu mae ḡihineꞌohe.
\p Badiꞌaꞌe vaze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa. Iniu vaze zamare borofeꞌenaꞌa, radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌa teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe, zu Badiꞌaꞌa ani teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe.
\v 17 Emeꞌa zamarotiteꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano, zamafe niduꞌa hina hube hune vaze zamare borofogaꞌe idaḡa. ꞌOugadu Badiꞌa kota madaḡano emeꞌe mene rihauꞌenaꞌa, ani ubumao edaꞌuma, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa haḡairoteꞌe teige eme zuni raha ꞌadao ꞌouge haḡae radiuꞌohe.
\v 18 Emeꞌa Badiꞌa zamare borofadu ani mene rihoneꞌohe. Hube hune ani zamare borofadu riho mae vaḡineꞌohe. Vazeꞌa ani mazaonoꞌo aduga hidiꞌuma radu rihauꞌohe. Rihauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zamaḡa niduꞌa hina Badiꞌa hube hune mene zamareꞌohe.
\v 19 Badiꞌaꞌa ibite geno emeḡe zamare borofiro ꞌahine, eme Badiꞌa zu vaze zamare borofeꞌohe.
\v 20 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa, “E Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌohe,” rae raenaꞌa, ane negoḡa nabuga heꞌeheꞌezine, aniꞌe ḡuriro vazeḡa. Horozeꞌeteꞌe negoḡa nabuga mene zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene horoneꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa zamare borofoga mene idaḡa.
\v 21 Emeꞌa Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo meiroteꞌe goroḡa ḡoeꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Iniuꞌa Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ane negoḡa nabuga zuni zamare borofiꞌuma.
\c 5
\s1 Iesuꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae mae Ḡihineꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa
\p 
\v 1 Iniu Iesuꞌe Keriso rae mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga. Iniu moga zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe moga ubuga zuni zamare borofeꞌohe.
\v 2 Eme Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌetene zu ane goro ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌetene, emeꞌa Badiꞌa ubugaubuga zamare borofeꞌetaꞌaꞌe edeḡa.
\v 3 Badiꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe ibiḡaꞌe ane goro ḡoeꞌa egohauꞌeteꞌe raꞌohe. Ane goro ḡoeꞌa egohanogaꞌe mene riḡa.
\v 4 Badiꞌa ubuga niduꞌaꞌe raha ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌohe. Emeꞌa fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, emeꞌe raha ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌohe.
\v 5 Raha ḡauḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iniu? Aꞌe, “Iesuꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga,” rae mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa daꞌo.
\s1 Iesu Kerisoꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae Fureniro
\p 
\v 6 Iesu Kerisoꞌe vu zu ru hina ariroteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe vu hina babatiso meiro zu ruḡa beꞌunadu rudaro. Aniꞌe mene vu hina daꞌo ariro, rehano vu zu ru hina ariro. Ebu Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa aniꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae fureneꞌohe, mazaḡa Vine Zaḡoḡaꞌe hugano ḡoereꞌohe.
\v 7 Iesuꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe uḡidu.
\v 8 Aꞌe, Vine Zaḡoḡa zu vu ebu ru. Uḡidu aꞌe Iesu moneo ḡoere idane rae fureneꞌohe.
\v 9 Eme vazeꞌa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mae ḡihineꞌohe. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa rae fureneꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa. Badiꞌaꞌa ane Ubuga moneo rae fureniro.
\v 10 Iniu Badiꞌa Ubuga mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ane zamao eꞌe. Iniu Badiꞌa mazao mene fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe, “Badiꞌaꞌe ḡuriro Badiꞌaḡa,” rae huniro, mazaḡa ani Badiꞌaꞌa ane Ubuga moneo rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mene mae ḡihiniro.
\v 11 Badiꞌaꞌa rae furenirotaꞌaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe: Aniꞌa ḡabone tuḡutuḡu rifiro ebu eꞌe ḡaboneḡaꞌe ane Ubuga zamaḡano radiuꞌohe.
\v 12 Iniu Ubuga mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡaboneḡeta, u iniu Badiꞌa Ubuga mene mae ḡihineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa mazaoꞌe ḡabone oꞌoꞌa.
\s1 Ḡabone Tuḡutuḡu
\p 
\v 13 Zaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga mazao fieꞌeteꞌe azaḡa. E zae veize ꞌahi miriheꞌohe. Ḡabone tuḡutuḡu zaeꞌa meirotaꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa ederifine soꞌa ꞌahi miriheꞌohe.
\v 14 Emeꞌa mene rihauꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa vaḡe onameꞌohe. Mazaḡa ani urao emeꞌa nagini umidine aniꞌa emeḡe uminone igiꞌuma rae edere huneꞌohe.
\v 15 Emeꞌa nagini umideꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa igiꞌohe. Eꞌe ederine, ani mazao nagini umidiroteꞌe emeꞌa hiditeꞌe zuni ederiꞌuma.
\p 
\v 16 Iniu negoḡaniꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe horoneꞌetene, haḡai sauꞌa eꞌeꞌa ani runeo mene tutuniꞌuma rae roꞌidene, Badiꞌa mazao kuranoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa runeo tutuzeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa sauꞌa mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡaboziꞌuma. U runeo tutuzeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa sauꞌaꞌe eꞌe. E haḡai sauꞌa ꞌuguḡa uꞌano kuranoꞌi rae mene raꞌohe.
\v 17 Haḡai veꞌoḡa niduꞌaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa. Rehano runeo mene tutuzeꞌeteꞌe haḡaiḡa sauꞌa zuni eꞌe.
\p 
\v 18 Eme edeḡa, Badiꞌa ubuga niduꞌaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa mene ꞌaune haḡaeꞌohe. Badiꞌa Ubuganiꞌa ze bireꞌeteꞌe uꞌano sauꞌa ḡauḡa, Sataniꞌa ze sausauzogaꞌe mene idaḡa.
\v 19 Eme edeḡa, emeꞌe Badiꞌa ubugaubuga ebu raha ꞌahi niduꞌaꞌe sauꞌa ḡauḡa Sataniꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.
\v 20 Zuni eme edeḡa, Badiꞌa Ubugaꞌe aradu zamarone manoḡa rifiro. ꞌOugadu emeḡeꞌa Badiꞌa huga edereꞌohe. Emeꞌe Badiꞌa huga teite tiburanadu radiuꞌohe ebu Ubuga Iesu Keriso teite zuni tiburanadu radiuꞌohe. Kerisoꞌe Badiꞌa huga zu ḡabone tuḡutuḡu.
\p 
\v 21 Tahiꞌatahiꞌa, ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi. \fig Ḡuriro badiꞌaḡa|src="WA04001b.tif" size="col" ref="5:21"\fig* 
